Constructor Detail

StringTokenizer

public StringTokenizer(java.lang.String line)
Creates a new instance of StringTokenizer. The delimiters are " \t\n\r\f" (first is space). Delimiters are not returned as tokens.

Parameters:
line - The string to be tokenized.

StringTokenizer

public StringTokenizer(java.lang.String line,
                       java.lang.String delimiters)
Creates a new instance of StringTokenizer with given delimiter chars . Delimiters are not returned as tokens.

Parameters:
line - The string to be tokenized.
delimiters - string containing delimiter chars
